Name: PV Standard Deviation
Formula:
//Define the time period that contains all in control capsules
$capsule = capsule('2020-10-15T18:54:25.253000+00:00', '2021-02-08T23:47:19.421000+00:00')
 
//Narrow down data to when process is in control, use keep() to filter the condition by the specific grade code capsule property
$Grade101 = $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 101')).intersect($inputcondition)
$Grade102 = $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 102')).intersect($inputcondition)
$Grade105 = $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 105')).intersect($inputcondition)
$Grade107 = $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 107')).intersect($inputcondition)
$Grade103 = $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 103')).intersect($inputcondition)
$Grade106 = $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 106')).intersect($inputcondition)
$Grade108 = $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 108')).intersect($inputcondition)
$Grade104 = $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 104')).intersect($inputcondition)

 
//Create stddev based on the times the product is in control, use .toDiscrete to create an unweighted stddev
$Grade101_stddev = $inputsignal.remove(not $Grade101).toDiscrete().stddev($capsule)$Grade102_stddev = $inputsignal.remove(not $Grade102).toDiscrete().stddev($capsule)$Grade105_stddev = $inputsignal.remove(not $Grade105).toDiscrete().stddev($capsule)$Grade107_stddev = $inputsignal.remove(not $Grade107).toDiscrete().stddev($capsule)$Grade103_stddev = $inputsignal.remove(not $Grade103).toDiscrete().stddev($capsule)$Grade106_stddev = $inputsignal.remove(not $Grade106).toDiscrete().stddev($capsule)$Grade108_stddev = $inputsignal.remove(not $Grade108).toDiscrete().stddev($capsule)$Grade104_stddev = $inputsignal.remove(not $Grade104).toDiscrete().stddev($capsule)
 
//Create stddev for all grades in one signal using splice(), use keep() to filter the condition by the specific grade code capsule property
//use within() to show only stddev only during the condition
0.splice($Grade101_stddev, $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 101')))
.splice($Grade102_stddev, $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 102')))
.splice($Grade105_stddev, $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 105')))
.splice($Grade107_stddev, $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 107')))
.splice($Grade103_stddev, $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 103')))
.splice($Grade106_stddev, $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 106')))
.splice($Grade108_stddev, $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 108')))
.splice($Grade104_stddev, $applytocondition.keep('Grade Code', isMatch('Grade 104')))
.within($applytocondition)
